{
	"modName": "PickmansWhisper",
	"displayName": "Pickman's Whisper",
	"minMcmVersion": 1,
	"plugin": "PickmansWhisper.esp",
	"content": [
		{
			"type": "spacer",
			"numLines": 2
		},
		{
			"text": "<p align='center'><font size='40'><b>Pickman's Whisper</b></font></p>",
			"type": "text",
			"html": true
		},
		{
			"text": "<p align='center'><font size='20'>Knife voice · serial hunger (not sexual)</font></p>",
			"type": "text",
			"html": true
		},
		{
			"text": "<p align='center'><font size='18'>Version 0.2.0 · Slice B</font></p>",
			"type": "text",
			"html": true
		},
		{
			"type": "spacer",
			"numLines": 1
		},
		{
			"text": "<p align='center'>Companion to <b>Necromantic</b>. Open <b>Debug</b> to verify F4SE / forms.</p>",
			"type": "text",
			"html": true
		}
	],
	"pages": [
		{
			"pageDisplayName": "How To Use",
			"content": [
				{
					"text": "Hook",
					"type": "section"
				},
				{
					"text": "Enter <b>Pickman Gallery</b> (interior) or obtain / equip <b>Pickman's Blade</b>. A voice bonds with the wielder — toast-only for Slice A.",
					"type": "text",
					"html": true
				},
				{
					"text": "Hunger",
					"type": "section"
				},
				{
					"text": "Once bonded, hunger rises with unused knife-time. High hunger applies <b>Knife Hunger</b> withdrawal (AGI/CHA −1). Kill a non-essential human with <b>Pickman's Blade</b> to sate hunger (praise toast + sated window).",
					"type": "text",
					"html": true
				},
				{
					"text": "Suite",
					"type": "section"
				},
				{
					"text": "Soft load order: Occult Pact → Pickman's Whisper → Necromantic. This mod is <b>not sexual</b>; Necromantic handles corpse scenes afterward.",
					"type": "text",
					"html": true
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"pageDisplayName": "Hunger",
			"content": [
				{
					"text": "Status",
					"type": "section"
				},
				{
					"id": "sBondState:Hunger",
